                           <locus/>Fol.32vb: Supplication for the donor(s) and for the "people of Ṗäraqliṭos". <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           Zä-Mikaʾel and his wife Fǝqǝrtä Krǝstos (but cp. Qǝddǝstä Krǝstos in the supplication formula on fol. 62ra) are mentioned. 
The note is written by the same hand as Additio 1 in AP-008.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus/>Fol.62rb: Excommunication against those who stole the book or erased its text.<q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           Written by the same hand as Additio 1 (?).
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title መ/. ግብረ ልኡካን "Mäṣḥafä gǝbrä lǝʾukan" is written on the front board with yellow modern paint.&#xD;
- Erasures: e.g., fols. 14vb, 24vb, 44va, 48va, 55rb.&#xD;
- Corrections written interlineally: fols. 13ra, 32rb, 32vb, sometimes in the main, sometimes in a secondary hand.&#xD;
- Crude note: fol. 62rb.&#xD;
- Crude doodles and drawings in recent hands, in ink, pen and pencil: e.g., fols. 1v, 2rv, 53v-57r, 59r, 129v, 130r.</item>
